* A closer look at that flamegraph

Run your code under instrumentation:

 $ go test -run=^$ -bench=BenchmarkReference -benchmem -cpuprofile prof.cpu
 BenchmarkReference-8   	     200	   9654082 ns/op	 1554625 B/op	   18844 allocs/op
 PASS
